  "texts": [
    "When using GPT, data quality (preferring a smaller but better data set over a larger but inaccurate one) is of prime importance (DataCamp, 2023b).",
    "Data labeling cannot be omitted.",
    "After property-based tagging (e.g.",
    "location data), access to data must consider the tag as well as predefined guidelines.",
    "This approach improves data management and simplifies the machine learning workflow (DataCamp, 2023b)."
  ]
}